text: Phryneta obliquata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Harold in 1878. It is known from Tanzania, Uganda, Somalia, the Democratic Republic of the Congo, Ethiopia and Kenya.BioLib.cz - Phryneta obliquata.
